1 (5) Any municipality eligible for a grant of assistance as provided
2 in this section may apply for a grant of assistance from the fund. Any
3 tribal government may apply for a grant of assistance from the fund.
4 Application shall be made on forms developed by the department.
5 Sec. 2. Original section 13-2706, Revised Statutes Cumulative
6 Supplement, 2024, is repealed.
